@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber

actor "System Administartor" as Employee
participant ":System" as System

activate Employee

    Employee -> System : asks to register a store
    activate System

        System --> Employee : requests data
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : types requested data (ID, designation/name, \n location,  phone number, e-mail address.)

    activate System



         System --> Employee : shows typed information and ask for confirmation
        deactivate System

        Employee -> System : confirms and submits data
        activate System

            System --> Employee : displays operation success
        deactivate System

@enduml